characterDescription: Jenet is the pretty, young, stablemaster of Dalinar Kholin..

characterDetails.Appearance: She is a lighteyed woman who wears a traditional Vorin gown. She wears her dark hair in a tail, without ornaments, and has a taughtness to her face.
characterDetails.Personality: Jenet is extremely protective of her horses and yet, expounding upon them, reveals herself to be vulnerable.
